data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!! This beautiful home can be a perfect starter home or an investor special!! This home is in a great location in a quiet neighborhood with NO HOA that sits in a 2 lot of .31 acres of living!! This home is close to downtown Lakeland and minutes to Southeastern University. The home features, 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, a living room family/great room, and 2 bonus rooms that can be converted into bedrooms. The open and spacious room with a vaulted ceiling in the great/family room has a wood-burning fireplace for cozy family time during the cold Winter Holiday Season! The French doors lead to the massive screened-in porch/patio for a relaxing with a hot cup of tea/coffee. The huge backyard has a chain-link and PVC fully fenced in for that special pet. This home is conveniently located close to Shopping Centers, Hospitals, and Clinics. This HOME will NOT last long!! Call me for a private showing TODAY!
